tatami.core.util.logging

Interface Log.ReportingEntity

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ClaimAgent, HierarchicalAgent, SimulationAgent, VisualizableAgent, VisualizationAgent, WSAgent
    Enclosing class:
    Log

    public static interface Log.ReportingEntity
    Interface for an entity / unit that keeps a log and that needs to report that log to other entities.
    Author:
    Andrei Olaru

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      boolean report(java.lang.String content)
      The function will be called at intervals of reportUpdateDelay, if new logging information exist since the last call.

    • Method Detail

      • report

        boolean report(java.lang.String content)
        The function will be called at intervals of reportUpdateDelay, if new logging information exist since the last call.
        Parameters:
        content - - an update from the log containing the new logging information since the last call of this function.
        Returns:
        true if the reporting has completed correctly. Otherwise, the same information will be reported again at the next call.
